<!doctype html>
<html>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href = "css/style1.css">
  <head>
    <title>Dragon!</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <img class = "background-dragon centered" style = "opacity: 0.15" src = "images/background-dragon.png">
    <img class="centered img_small" style = "top: 10%;" src="images/Title.png">
    <center><p class="centered" style = "top: 40%;"><b>And so the story begins… As you are enjoying a tasty snack munching on some mutton a knight approaches. “Stop taking our cattle Dragon!” he says. He has insulted you because you are not just a Dragon. You are The mighty (name).<br><br>Option #1: I whip him with my (skin_type) tail and have him as a snack <br><br>Option #2: I don't bother myself with such puny adversaries I take to the air with the beat of my (skin type) wings</b></p></center>
    <img class="centered img_small" style = "top: 80%;" src="images/knight.png">
    <form method = "POST" action = "page2">
